{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
    "name": "FOXAI System Service (gRPC)",
    "description": "Payload reference + endpoint catalog for FOXAI System Service (.NET 9 + gRPC).\n\n**Cách dùng:**\n1. Khởi động service (`pnpm --filter @foxai/system-service dev`) — listen `localhost:51051`.\n2. Mở `Login` request, copy payload từ Body → tạo gRPC Request mới trong Postman (`New → gRPC Request`), URL `localhost:51051`, **Use server reflection: ON**.\n3. Chọn service `foxai.system.AuthService` → method `Login` → paste payload → Invoke.\n4. Copy `access_token` từ response sang environment variable `accessToken`.\n5. Các request authenticated khác đã có sẵn metadata `authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}`.\n\n**Note:** Các item bên dưới mô phỏng request gRPC dưới dạng REST `POST` với URL `grpc://...`. Postman không tự invoke được gRPC từ format này — đây là **payload reference**. Để invoke thực sự, dùng Postman gRPC Request riêng + reflection (đã enable ở Development mode).\n\nXem [README](https://github.com/your-org/foxai-native/blob/main/docs/postman/README.md) để biết thêm chi tiết.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "00 - Smoke test",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health (REST /health)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{healthUrl}}",
              "host": ["{{healthUrl}}"]
            },
            "description": "Endpoint REST duy nhất — kiểm tra service + DB connectivity.\n\n**Expected response:**\n```\nHealthy\n```\n\nNếu trả `Unhealthy` thì DB connection có vấn đề (kiểm tra Postgres + connection string)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (seeded admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "// Script này chỉ chạy nếu request thực thi như HTTP/REST (sẽ fail vì là gRPC).",
                  "// Khi dùng Postman gRPC Request thật, copy script này vào tab Scripts:",
                  "//",
                  "// const resp = pm.response.json();",
                  "// pm.environment.set('accessToken', resp.access_token);",
                  "// pm.environment.set('refreshToken', resp.refresh_token);",
                  "// pm.environment.set('adminUserId', resp.user.id);",
                  "// console.log('Tokens saved to environment.');"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.AuthService/Login",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.AuthService", "Login"]
            },
            "description": "# AuthService.Login\n\n**gRPC:** `foxai.system.AuthService/Login`\n\n**Body:**\n```json\n{\n  \"email\": \"admin@foxai.local\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin@12345\"\n}\n```\n\n**Expected response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"accessToken\": \"eyJhbGc...\",\n  \"refreshToken\": \"...\",\n  \"expiresIn\": 604800,\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": \"<guid>\",\n    \"email\": \"admin@foxai.local\",\n    \"fullName\": \"System Administrator\",\n    \"roles\": [\"SUPER_ADMIN\"],\n    \"permissions\": [\"USER_CREATE\", \"SYSTEM_ADMIN\", ...]\n  }\n}\n```\n\nSau khi login thành công, copy `accessToken` sang environment variable `accessToken`."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "01 - Auth (4 RPC)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.AuthService/Login",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.AuthService", "Login"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.AuthService/Login`\n\nCấp JWT access token (7d) + refresh token (30d). Refresh token lưu hash SHA256 trong DB, rotate-on-use.\n\n**Errors:**\n- `UNAUTHENTICATED`: Email/password sai hoặc user không phải `ACTIVE`\n- `INVALID_ARGUMENT`: Email format sai hoặc field rỗng"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "RefreshToken",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.AuthService/RefreshToken",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.AuthService", "RefreshToken"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.AuthService/RefreshToken`\n\nRotate refresh token: token cũ bị revoke + token mới phát hành. Response giống `Login`.\n\n**Errors:**\n- `UNAUTHENTICATED`: Token không tồn tại, đã revoke, hoặc expired"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "ValidateToken",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"accessToken\": \"{{accessToken}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.AuthService/ValidateToken",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.AuthService", "ValidateToken"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.AuthService/ValidateToken`\n\nVerify HS256 signature + expiry + load user fresh. Trả `valid: true/false` + user profile (nếu valid).\n\nThường gọi bởi API Gateway sau khi nhận request từ client. API Gateway có thể tự verify bằng cùng `JWT_SECRET` thay vì gọi RPC này."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.AuthService/Logout",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.AuthService", "Logout"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.AuthService/Logout`\n\nRevoke refresh token cụ thể. Idempotent — gọi nhiều lần đều OK."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "02 - Users (9 RPC)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "CreateUser",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{testUserEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{testUserPassword}}\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Test User\",\n  \"phone\": \"+84-901-234-567\",\n  \"roleCodes\": [\"USER\"]\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.UsersService/CreateUser",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.UsersService", "CreateUser"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.UsersService/CreateUser`\n\n**Rules:**\n- Email unique, format chuẩn, ≤ 254 chars\n- Password ≥ 8 chars, có chữ + số\n- `organizationId` (optional) phải tồn tại\n- `roleCodes` (optional) phải tồn tại trong DB\n\n**Errors:**\n- `ALREADY_EXISTS`: Email đã dùng\n- `INVALID_ARGUMENT`: Validation fail\n- `NOT_FOUND`: org_id hoặc role_code không tồn tại\n\n**Sau khi tạo:** Copy `id` từ response sang env var `testUserId`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GetUser",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"{{testUserId}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.UsersService/GetUser",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.UsersService", "GetUser"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.UsersService/GetUser`\n\nTrả về `UserDto` đầy đủ kèm `roles[]`.\n\n**Errors:**\n- `NOT_FOUND`: User id không tồn tại"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "ListUsers (paginated)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"pagination\": {\n    \"page\": 1,\n    \"pageSize\": 20,\n    \"search\": \"\",\n    \"sortBy\": \"createdAt\",\n    \"sortOrder\": \"desc\"\n  },\n  \"status\": \"\",\n  \"organizationId\": \"\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.UsersService/ListUsers",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.UsersService", "ListUsers"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.UsersService/ListUsers`\n\n**Pagination:**\n- `page` 1-based, mặc định 1\n- `pageSize` 1-100, mặc định 20\n- `search` ILIKE trên email + fullName\n- `sortBy`: `createdAt` (default) | `email` | `fullName`\n- `sortOrder`: `asc` | `desc`\n\n**Filters:**\n- `status`: ACTIVE | INACTIVE | LOCKED (rỗng = tất cả)\n- `organizationId`: filter theo org trực tiếp (không bao gồm sub-orgs)\n\n**Response:** `{ items: [...], page: { page, pageSize, totalItems, totalPages } }`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "UpdateUser",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"{{testUserId}}\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Updated Name\",\n  \"phone\": \"+84-987-654-321\",\n  \"avatarUrl\": \"https://example.com/avatar.png\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.UsersService/UpdateUser",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.UsersService", "UpdateUser"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.UsersService/UpdateUser`\n\nFields cho phép update: `fullName`, `phone`, `avatarUrl`, `organizationId`. Email **không** đổi được qua RPC này.\n\nMọi field optional — chỉ field nào set mới update.\n\n**Errors:**\n- `NOT_FOUND`: User hoặc org không tồn tại"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "DeleteUser (soft → INACTIVE)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"{{testUserId}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.UsersService/DeleteUser",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.UsersService", "DeleteUser"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.UsersService/DeleteUser`\n\nSoft delete: set `status = INACTIVE` + revoke tất cả refresh tokens. Không xóa khỏi DB để giữ FK history."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "ChangePassword",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"{{testUserId}}\",\n  \"oldPassword\": \"Test@12345\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"NewPass@67890\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.UsersService/ChangePassword",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.UsersService", "ChangePassword"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.UsersService/ChangePassword`\n\nRequire `oldPassword` verify. Sau khi đổi: **revoke tất cả refresh tokens** của user (force re-login).\n\n**Errors:**\n- `UNAUTHENTICATED`: Old password sai\n- `INVALID_ARGUMENT`: New password yếu hoặc trùng cũ"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "ChangeStatus",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"{{testUserId}}\",\n  \"status\": \"LOCKED\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.UsersService/ChangeStatus",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.UsersService", "ChangeStatus"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.UsersService/ChangeStatus`\n\nValid status: `ACTIVE` | `INACTIVE` | `LOCKED` (case insensitive).\n\nKhi đổi sang `LOCKED` hoặc `INACTIVE`: revoke tất cả refresh tokens."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "AssignRole",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"{{testUserId}}\",\n  \"roleCode\": \"ADMIN\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.UsersService/AssignRole",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.UsersService", "AssignRole"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.UsersService/AssignRole`\n\nIdempotent — gán role đã có thì skip."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "UnassignRole",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"{{testUserId}}\",\n  \"roleCode\": \"ADMIN\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.UsersService/UnassignRole",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.UsersService", "UnassignRole"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.UsersService/UnassignRole`\n\n**Business rule:** Không cho remove role `SUPER_ADMIN` cuối cùng còn lại trong hệ thống → trả `FAILED_PRECONDITION`."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "03 - Roles (7 RPC)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "CreateRole",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"{{testRoleCode}}\",\n  \"name\": \"Test Role\",\n  \"description\": \"Vai trò dùng cho test\",\n  \"permissionCodes\": [\"USER_READ\", \"ROLE_READ\"]\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.RolesService/CreateRole",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.RolesService", "CreateRole"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.RolesService/CreateRole`\n\n**Rules:**\n- `code` UPPER_SNAKE_CASE: `^[A-Z][A-Z0-9_]*$`\n- `permissionCodes` (optional) phải tồn tại\n- Role tạo qua RPC này luôn có `isSystem = false`\n\n**Errors:**\n- `ALREADY_EXISTS`: code đã dùng\n- `INVALID_ARGUMENT`: code format sai\n\nSau khi tạo: copy `id` sang env var `testRoleId`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GetRole",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"{{testRoleId}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.RolesService/GetRole",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.RolesService", "GetRole"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.RolesService/GetRole`\n\nTrả `RoleDto` kèm `permissions[]`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "ListRoles",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"pagination\": {\n    \"page\": 1,\n    \"pageSize\": 50\n  },\n  \"includePermissions\": true\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.RolesService/ListRoles",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.RolesService", "ListRoles"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.RolesService/ListRoles`\n\n`includePermissions = true` → eager-load permissions per role (tốn 1 query bằng Include). False → chỉ metadata role."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "UpdateRole",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"{{testRoleId}}\",\n  \"name\": \"Updated Role Name\",\n  \"description\": \"Updated description\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.RolesService/UpdateRole",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.RolesService", "UpdateRole"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.RolesService/UpdateRole`\n\nChỉ cho update `name` + `description`. `code` và `isSystem` không đổi được."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "DeleteRole",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"{{testRoleId}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.RolesService/DeleteRole",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.RolesService", "DeleteRole"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.RolesService/DeleteRole`\n\n**Errors:**\n- `FAILED_PRECONDITION`: `isSystem = true` (SUPER_ADMIN, ADMIN, USER) hoặc còn user dùng role này"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "AssignPermissions",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"roleId\": \"{{testRoleId}}\",\n  \"permissionCodes\": [\"USER_CREATE\", \"USER_UPDATE\", \"ORG_READ\"]\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpcUrl}}/foxai.system.RolesService/AssignPermissions",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.RolesService", "AssignPermissions"]
            },
