              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["foxai.system.OrganizationsService", "CreateNode"]
            },
            "description": "**gRPC:** `foxai.system.OrganizationsService/CreateNode`\n\n**Tree logic:**\n- Không có `parentId` → root, `level = 0`, `path = /<code>`\n- Có `parentId` → `level = parent.level + 1`, `path = parent.path + /<code>`\n\n**Rules:**\n- `code`: `^[A-Za-z][A-Za-z0-9_-]*$` (cho phép `kebab-case`)\n- Unique toàn DB\n\nLưu `id` vào env var `testOrgId`."
          }
